title: Prequel
subtitle: Prenatal Screen
summary: Determine a risk of a fetus
detailsDescription: A prenatal Cell Free DNA (pcfDNA) screen that can determine if a pregnancy is at an increased risk for chromosomal conditions like Down, Edwards or Patau syndromes, and provides the predicated fetal sex.

benefits.description: Most patients are covered by insurance and pay $0.
Direct payment options and financial assistance are available for qualified individuals.
